<section class="py-12 md:py-24">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 md:px-6">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      <h1 class="font-display text-4xl md:text-6xl mb-6 leading-tight">
        From Scaling Search Engines to Tracking the "Sacred Guide"
      </h1>

      <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 mb-12 leading-relaxed">
        I’m Sébastien Loix. I spent years as a Principal Engineer at Elastic, but in late 2024, I decided to resign and bet entirely on my own investment strategy. This tool is the result of that transition.
      </p>

      <div class="prose prose-lg">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-display mt-10">The "Why" Behind the Project</h2>
        <p>
          When I began managing my portfolio full-time, I hit a wall. I couldn’t find a single tool online that allowed me to truly analyze my trade history. I needed to know: <em>"If I sell today in 2026, which specific shares from 2022 am I selling, and what is my actual tax liability?"</em>
        </p>
        <p>
          Beyond that, most trackers forced me to choose between an "equity tracker," a "crypto app," or a "manual spreadsheet." I needed a single source of truth that unified <strong>Spot Equity, Options, and Crypto</strong> in one place.
        </p>

        <blockquote class="border-l-4 border-emerald-500 pl-4 italic my-8">
          "I built this because it was going to be my 'sacred guide' to ensure I don’t have to worry about money until I turn 120."
        </blockquote>

        <h2 class="text-3xl font-display mt-10">The Philosophy: Where the Puck is Going</h2>
        <p>
          My investment journey changed when I found the <strong>InvestAnswers</strong> community. If you don't know James, you should check out his YouTube channel. His dedication to sharing knowledge on finance, macro, and market positioning is unmatched.
        </p>
        <p>
          James taught me the importance of <strong>positioning yourself where the puck is going to be</strong>. To do that effectively, you need clear data. You need to be able to make decisions quickly without wrestling with your spreadsheet for hours.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-3xl font-display mt-10">Optimizing for Freedom (and Taxes)</h2>
        <p>
          Living off investments requires discipline, and a big part of that is controlling your environment. I eventually moved to <strong>Andorra</strong>. It offers the perfect balance of beautiful nature and safety, while being a tax-friendly jurisdiction perfectly situated between France and Spain.
        </p>
        <p>
          This environment allows me to focus on what matters: refining this tool and my portfolio.
        </p>

        <div class="bg-emerald-50 p-8 rounded-2xl my-12 border border-emerald-100">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-display mb-4 text-emerald-900">The Mission & Commitment</h3>
          <p class="text-emerald-800">
            This project is, first and foremost, a tool I built for myself. It is now in <strong>public beta</strong> and available to everyone with a <strong>free premium license valid for 1 year</strong>.
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-2 text-emerald-800">
            <li><strong>No Data-Mining:</strong> Your data stays in your Google Sheet.</li>
            <li><strong>No Data-Sharing:</strong> I sell software, not your personal information.</li>
            <li><strong>Simplicity + Power:</strong> A tool that is simple enough to use daily, but powerful enough to handle complex tax and history analysis.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <p class="text-center mt-12">
          <a href="/pricing" class="inline-block bg-emerald-600 text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-full font-bold hover:bg-emerald-700 transition-colors">
            Get Your Free License
          </a>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

